    "body": "Thanks for the response.\n\nPerhaps you can comment on this behavior?\n\n``` python\n>>> df.loc[0,[1,2]]\n1    1\n2    2\nName: 0, dtype: object\n>>> df.loc[0,[1,2]] = [3,4]\n>>> df\n   1  2  a\n0  1  3  4\n1  1  2  a\n\n[2 rows x 3 columns]\n```\n\nApparently loc selects a different part of the dataframe for getting than it does for setting?\n"
